sequenceDiagram
    participant Q as Query Node (DID_q)
    participant O as Oracle (DID_o)
    Note over Q: Generate ephemeral X25519 keypair (eph_sk, eph_pk)
    Q->>Q: nonce = random(16)
    Q->>Q: ts = now_ns()
    Q->>Q: msg = canonical(DID_q, ctx, cluster, eph_pk, ts, nonce)
    Q->>Q: sig = Ed25519.sign(msg, DID_q)
    Q->>O: POST /issue { request, signature }
    O->>O: Resolve DID_q -> Ed25519 pubkey (did:key, no network)
    O->>O: Verify signature
    O->>O: Check |now - ts| <= 60s
    O->>O: Check nonce not in replay cache
    O->>O: Look up grant in ledger (now=ts)
    alt grant valid
        O->>O: cell_key = HKDF(master, ctx || cluster)
        O->>O: oracle_eph_sk, oracle_eph_pk = X25519.gen()
        O->>O: shared = X25519(oracle_eph_sk, eph_pk)
        O->>O: sym = HKDF(shared)
        O->>O: ct = AES-GCM(sym, cell_key, AAD=msg)
        O-->>Q: 200 { oracle_eph_pk, nonce, ct }
        Q->>Q: shared' = X25519(eph_sk, oracle_eph_pk)
        Q->>Q: sym' = HKDF(shared')
        Q->>Q: cell_key = AES-GCM.decrypt(sym', ct, AAD=msg)
    else grant absent / revoked
        O-->>Q: 403 { reason }
    else auth/replay/skew failure
        O-->>Q: 401
    end
